abstract: New York Yankees veteran Jorge Posada is emotional following playoff loss to Detroit Tigers, considering that he may have played his final game with team.
snippet: Jorge Posada had two hits Thursday night and batted .429 against the Tigers in the division series, but he may have played his last game as a Yankee.
lead_paragraph: Jorge Posada had two hits Thursday night and batted .429 against the Tigers in the division series, but he may have played his last game as a Yankee.

headline.seo: Jorge Posada Emotional After Possible Final Game as a Yankee
